"title": "5295: destruction",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "5295: destruction",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>The demolition or eradication of buildings, peoples or individuals. Since God is the Creator and sustainer of all things, wanton ruin is contrary to his will as his original purposes cannot be fulfilled. God will bring about the final destruction of all that is evil in the last judgment.</p>\n<h2>God disapproves of wanton destruction</h2>\n<h3>Of human life</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod20:13\">EXO 20:13</a></strong> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut5:17\">DEU 5:17</a> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen4:8-Gen4:12\">GEN 4:8–4:12</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen9:5-Gen9:6\">GEN 9:5–9:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam12:7-2Sam12:10\">2SA 12:7–12:10</a></p>\n<h3>Of the world in general</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev11:18\">REV 11:18</a></strong> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen1:28\">GEN 1:28</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen2:15\">GEN 2:15</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut20:19-Deut20:20\">DEU 20:19–20:20</a></p>\n<h3>Of spiritual life</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom14:15\">ROM 14:15</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor8:9-1Cor8:11\">1CO 8:9–8:11</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Tim2:17-2Tim2:18\">2TI 2:17–2:18</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Pet2:1\">2PE 2:1</a></p>\n<h2>Agents of destruction</h2>\n<h3>Satan</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job1:12-Job1:19\">JOB 1:12–1:19</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John8:44\">JHN 8:44</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John10:10\">JHN 10:10</a></p>\n<h3>The wicked</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps55:11\">PSA 55:11</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov1:10-Prov1:12\">PRO 1:10–1:12</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke13:1-Luke13:3\">LUK 13:1–13:3</a></p>\n<h3>Nature</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt6:19\">MAT 6:19</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke13:4-Luke13:5\">LUK 13:4–13:5</a></p>\n<h2>God himself brings destruction on the wicked</h2>\n<h3>God decrees destruction for sinners</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps37:38\">PSA 37:38</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen6:5-Gen6:7\">GEN 6:5–6:7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps5:6\">PSA 5:6</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps46:8\">PSA 46:8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa34:2\">ISA 34:2</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Amos1:3-Amos1:8\">AMO 1:3–1:8</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Amos2:1-Amos2:3\">AMO 2:1–2:3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke3:9\">LUK 3:9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1John3:8\">1JN 3:8</a></p>\n<h3>By the forces of nature</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen7:4\">GEN 7:4</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen19:24-Gen19:25\">GEN 19:24–19:25</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut28:15-Deut28:24\">DEU 28:15–28:24</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps48:7\">PSA 48:7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek5:16\">EZK 5:16</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek13:13\">EZK 13:13</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke17:29\">LUK 17:29</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev6:12-Rev6:14\">REV 6:12–6:14</a></p>\n<h3>By means of angels</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor10:10\">1CO 10:10</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod12:23\">EXO 12:23</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam24:15-2Sam24:17\">2SA 24:15–24:17</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Chr21:14-1Chr21:17\">1CH 21:14–21:17</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Chr21:12\">1CH 21:12</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs19:35\">2KI 19:35</a> parallels <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr32:21\">2CH 32:21</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa37:36\">ISA 37:36</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts12:23\">ACT 12:23</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev7:2-Rev7:3\">REV 7:2–7:3</a></p>\n<h3>By means of human beings</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut7:16\">DEU 7:16</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num21:3\">NUM 21:3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut2:34\">DEU 2:34</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut3:6\">DEU 3:6</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut28:47-Deut28:48\">DEU 28:47–28:48</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Josh6:21\">JOS 6:21</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Josh8:26\">JOS 8:26</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Josh11:20\">JOS 11:20</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer25:9\">JER 25:9</a></p>\n<h3>Destruction in the final judgment</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Thess1:8-2Thess1:9\">2TH 1:8–1:9</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mal4:1\">MAL 4:1</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Thess2:8\">2TH 2:8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev17:8\">REV 17:8</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev17:11\">REV 17:11</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev18:21\">REV 18:21</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev20:10\">REV 20:10</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev20:14\">REV 20:14</a></p>\n<h3>Destruction is sudden</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Thess5:3\">1TH 5:3</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov6:15\">PRO 6:15</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov24:21-Prov24:22\">PRO 24:21–24:22</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov29:1\">PRO 29:1</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eccl9:12\">ECC 9:12</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa30:13\">ISA 30:13</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa47:11\">ISA 47:11</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer15:8\">JER 15:8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Pet3:10\">2PE 3:10</a></p>\n<h3>Warnings against the way of destruction</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt7:13\">MAT 7:13</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Josh6:18\">JOS 6:18</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Tim6:9\">1TI 6:9</a></p>\n<h2>God keeps his people from destruction</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod12:13\">EXO 12:13</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps91:9-Ps91:10\">PSA 91:9–91:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom8:35-Rom8:39\">ROM 8:35–8:39</a></p>\n<h2>God's kingdom is indestructible</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb12:28\">HEB 12:28</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps46:5\">PSA 46:5</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps125:1\">PSA 125:1</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan2:44\">DAN 2:44</a></p>\n<h2>There will be no destruction in the world to come</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa11:9\">ISA 11:9</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan7:27\">DAN 7:27</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev21:3-Rev21:5\">REV 21:3–21:5</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev22:15\">REV 22:15</a></p>",
